text: Ali Abdul-Jabbar Al-Saadi () is an Iraqi professional footballer who plays as a defender and is the captain of Al Quwa Al Jawiya club. ==Coaching career== ===Al-Quwa Al-Jawiya=== Luay Salah started as an assistant coach to Ayoub Odisho in Al-Quwa Al-Jawiya in march of 2019. ==Honours== *AFC Cup: 2016http://www.the- afc.com/afcasfeeds?fixtureid=10495&stageid;=413&tMode;=H&view;=ajax&show;=matchsummary *Iraq FA Cup: 2015–16 * Iraqi Premier League: 16-17 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:AFC Cup winning players
